content:
Set Up Routing and Rules in Service Cloud

Unify your channels and manage your agent workload with Omni-Channel routing. Set up rules and queues to automate your service process.

Route Work with Omni-Channel:
Use Omni-Channel to manage priority of work items, route important items to agents quickly, and define which agents can handle different types of assignments.

Automate Case Processing with Rules:
Set up rules to prioritize, distribute, assign, respond to, and escalate records.

Route Work with Einstein Case Routing:
Save agents time with Einstein. When Einstein updates a field on a case, run assignment rules to route the case to an agent.
